                                   Desk_Error2_VerboseExit, to avoid pulling in
                                   the rather large Desk_Error2_VerboseExit
                                   function.
             1.02 (29 Nov 1995) JS Now passes Desk_error2_block* in call to 
                                   longjmp()
             1.03 (13 Dec 1995) JS Added Desk_jumpauto_lasterror.
